    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Applied clothing accessories that may be made of rope, ribbon or fabric. These consist of knots with two loops and two ends, fixed into decorative elements attached to clothing or other objects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
